# /src/ (main source code)
# /tests/ (rust test files)
# /benches/ (rust benchmarks) 
# /examples/ (rust examples)
# Cargo.toml
# Cargo.lock
# LICENSE
# README.md
# CHANGELOG.md
# CLAUDE.md (critical rules)
